Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不正常起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.15,0:02:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 快 要快逃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是两人一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是友好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子 让人觉得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个时空的鸦见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着这个准备做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准备这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 已经结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样打烂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 拜托你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有着一样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那眼神让我厌恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个时空的鸦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 在动了 走吧 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时空还没有安定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要被那样的家伙盯上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶上被...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 快抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 你就是那样抢走别人的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了遮罩用量子自旋壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩要掉下去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想死的话就坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你战斗的气概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是做不到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连生存的力量都没有的人就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一样的顽固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍眼啊 那不服的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田啊 有没有弄错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回去了吧 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定原因在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个山里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 就这点程度 也贴了OK绷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走一会就停下问我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 头上受伤了 脚也很疼不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小...小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能载我们到山下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这之前的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出鸟儿返回鸟巢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹大麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还作为异常者被强制回收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧 龙之转矩怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要着急 枭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时空留下我们的痕迹才是危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个时空也出现了扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 必须要找到鸦的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是为了不留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是脚被带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象被这个时空讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我会相信那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚还出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真是觉得丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时禁止去私塾以外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去私塾的时候由我来接送
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 光飞走了 你认为那究竟是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道在外面晃到那么晚 才会碰到那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算暑假 晚上也不能老到外面去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有胡说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像遥那么大的时候 也经常幻想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有令人期待心砰砰直跳的事情发生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦是那个人的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小孩 看上去不像在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有被破坏啊 哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是来看夜景的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏的空间修复顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的好 鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭 鸦的位置明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反映 但座标无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还存在于这个时空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正处于衰弱状态 所以座标无法稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住手 不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经错乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理许可已经收到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种错乱非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十皇会那里肯定很啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微冒些风险也是没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了绝对座标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个来了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛 拉库利玛...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要消失了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住...住手 请住手 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有登啊 哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视里的新闻里也没有报导啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网路上也没有类似消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缆车的绳索还好好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小的时候就一直看到碰到奇怪的东西对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 灵异体质？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近没有怎么看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 为什么后藤会被盯上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天也被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 在坟地和大家分散以后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥和后藤君两人单独在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会你们两个在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才...才不是呢 怎么突然变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他只是普通的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.82,0:18:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保从以前开始 就一直喜欢后藤了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击 已经倒下站不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 美保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤就让给遥吧 好朋友么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我将找到新的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 不愧是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油美保
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不要和那孩子见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也明白吧 现在是重要时期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 四 五 六 七 八 九 十
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的时候和佑在一起玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 还要喝水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再去拿一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又以佑为目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获龙之转矩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目标不是那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.34,0:23:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.14,0:24:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏天的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺因 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.91,0:24:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥总有一天要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.30,0:25:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 我最讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭

